<p><span style="font-size: 14pt"></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14pt"><img src="/uploads/2021/12/ce24fe4f022d7c2428f14b2a51778230.png"></span><br><span style="font-size: 14pt"></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14pt">尝试读取默认文件 &#x2F;etc&#x2F;passwd</span></p>
